Crystal and Meg Ryan as best friends who become lovers, was in
sixth with earnings of $2 million. In seventh was the Bruce Willis
Vietnam movie ``In Country,'' with admissions of $1.369 million.
   Next was the independent film ``sex, lies and videotape,'' which
collected $1.368 million.
