screens, $1,688 per screen, $80.8 million, 12 weeks.
   7. ``In Country,'' Warner Bros., $1.369 million, 606 screens,
$2,260 per screen, $1.5 million, three weeks.
   8. ``sex, lies and videotape,'' Miramax, $1.368 million, 534
screens, $2,563 per screen, $17.2 million, nine weeks.
