relationship was ``one of the great love affairs of all time.'' The
couple had known each other in Budapest but did not become
romantically involved until meeting again in this country, she said.
   De Szigethy operated his wife's jewelry store in New York City.
   Zsa Zsa Gabor made several visits to the desert to comfort her
mother and ailing stepfather during the actress' celebrated
cop-slapping trial in Beverly Hills.
   She was convicted of battery Friday and faces a possible
18-month jail term when sentenced Oct. 17.
   A private funeral was planned.
