<HEAD>Bomb Explosion Shatters Windows in Turkish Sector</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NICOSIA, Cyprus (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A bomb exploded outside an apartment
building in the Turkish sector of Nicosia early Tuesday, shattering
windows but causing no injuries.
   The explosion occurred just after midnight.
   Alpay Durduran, an independent deputy in the unicameral
Parliament of the Turkish Republic of Northern Cyprus, lives in one
