Republican Turkish Party found a bomb in front of the party
offices, said party leader Ozker Ozgur.
   It was deactivated before it exploded.
   Cyprus has been divided into northern Turkish and southern Greek
Cypriot sectors since Turkish troops invaded the island following
an Athens-backed coup in 1974.
