<HEAD>United Jet Reports Engine Fire, Returns Safely</HEAD>
<DATELINE>CHICAGO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The pilot of a United Airlines jet reported a
fire in the tail engine moments after takeoff early today but
returned the plane safely to O'Hare International Airport,
authorities said.
   No fire was found and no injuries were reported among the 77
