oil and natural gas reserves through its Texas Oil &amp; Gas Corp.
subsidiary, and analysts have estimated USX could get $1.5 billion
in the sale.
   Among other blue chip issues, Boeing was up 2 to 58| as the
company's unionized machinists voted on whether to accept a
three-year contract offer or reaffirm a midnight strike deadline.
   IBM was off 2 to 106|, American Express was up 1[ to 37[ and
General Electric rose \ to 58.
   The NYSE's composite index of all its listed common stocks
gained 1.15 to 196.05. At the American Stock Exchange, the market
value index was up 2.09 at 391.75.
